These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
City: rome, prague, boston, san-francisco, hannover, london
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| City      | prague  | london | hannover | rome | san-francisco | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, ship, tram, helicopter, trike, car
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person driving the car is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
9. the person driving the train is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Transport   | train   | trike | ship | car | helicopter     | tram  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
6 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, horse, goldfish, rat, dog
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the german##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the polish##1
6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the owner of the goldfish##1
9. the owner of the horse is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Pet   | goldfish   | dog   | rat      | hamster | hedgehog  | horse   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

