.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, russian, italian, indian
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, electronic, house, techno
 1. the fan of disco is the american##1
 2. the argentine is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the colombian##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the argentine##1
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 7. the indian is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the american is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
10. the russian is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Nationality         | russian | indian | american | italian | argentine | colombian  |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | electronic  | disco  | classical | house      | country |

