.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, pall-mall, swisher, aristoff, dannemann, old-henry
There are 6 different nationalities: american, australian, brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
1. the mexican is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the american##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the australian is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the german is the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
9. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Cigar   | old-henry    | swisher    | ritmeester | dannemann     | pall-mall   | aristoff     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

