.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, guinea-pig, horse, snake, turtle
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, coffee, hot-chocolate, 7up, iced-tea
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Beverage   | cola | 7up | iced-tea | coffee     | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate       |

