.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, turtle, fish, frog, rabbit
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the owner of the turtle is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Pet   | rabbit | bird  | frog     | turtle    | goldfish  | fish          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

