.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, ship, airplane, helicopter, bus
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
9. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | motorbike | bus | helicopter | ship | airplane |

