.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
There are 6 different nationalities: british, dutch, french, indian, polish, spanish
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, may, july, september, april, february
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
2. the indian is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the polish##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the indian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
7. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the spanish##1
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Nationality   | polish | spanish | indian    | dutch | french  | british |
| Birthday     | may    | april | september | february   | july | october    |

