The people use 6 different means of transport: car, motorbike, roller, scooter, tram, trike
1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the roller##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
9. the havana-smoker is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Cigar         | aristoff | bluemaster | old-henry | ritmeester | dannemann    | havana |
| Transport   | car   | tram      | scooter        | roller    | motorbike | trike  |

