.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-14::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, magic-tricks, puzzles, skydiving, traveling
6 different games are played: poker, snooker, go, backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |    4    |      5       |     6     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving | drawing | puzzles | magic-tricks | traveling |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | snooker      | backgammon    | poker    | monopoly        | go     |

