.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-15::.
There 6 different types of food: grapefruit, grapes, lemon, onion, peach, pineapple
6 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, domino, poker, whist, mah-jongg
1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
3. the person eating lemon is the person playing poker##1
4. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating onion is the person playing billiard##1
6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person playing domino is the person eating pineapple##1
8. the person playing whist is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
9. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Food        | lemon     | peach | grapes   | onion      | pineapple | grapefruit |
| Game   | poker | whist  | backgammon | billiard | domino   | mah-jongg     |

