.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-16::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles, reading, rock-climbing
House: ranch-style, wooden, gothic-revival, palace, farmhouse, modern
1. the modern house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the ranch-style house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the palace house##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
7. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Hobby   | reading | magic-tricks | fishing  | rock-climbing | puzzles       | hiking   |
| House   | gothic-revival | wooden     | ranch-style | farmhouse        | palace | modern |

