.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-19::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, blood-red, apricot, fuchsia, orange, purple
The people have 6 different jobs:  chef, lawyer, manager, police-officer, project-manager, scientist
1. the person who likes fuchsia is the manager##1
2. the scientist is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the manager##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the scientist##1
6. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes purple is the project-manager##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
9. the chef is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |   3    |     4      |      5       |    6    |
| Color   | orange        | purple     | red  | apricot | fuchsia | blood-red |
| Job     | police-officer | project-manager | lawyer | scientist  | manager      | chef    |

