.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
6 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, dog, rat, goldfish, snake
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
9. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| Pet     | snake  | bird | hedgehog | rat | goldfish  | dog |

 